Today I got to meet the man behind the plan that kicked off my 30 day project. Meet Andrew.

I like his spirit. He has some nice ink too commemorating his marriage and his children. It made me feel all warm and fuzzy inside,

I'm such a ham. I gave Andrew the camera and let him take a few snaps of me. I'm always ready for my close up Mr. DeVille.

There was even an attempt to bite my head. I have that effect on people. :-)


All in all, it was a nice lunch and I got to connect with another like minded person. Win. I know some amazing folks (you know who you are) and I look forward to meeting more nifty people in the future. Have a good Sunday peeps.
